title: Picnic Time's Malibu 508
transcripts: The Malibu by picnic time is the most convenient universal go anywhere picnic tote. Fully insulated, it's made of 600 denier polyester with a 12 can capacity. It comes with deluxe picnic service for two. The Malibu features a separate insulated divided wine section with peek though closures for to toll bottles and a removable water resistant liner in the food storage area. it includes two 9 inch melamine plates, two glasses, four cotton napkins, two stainless steel knives, forks and spoons , a six inch hardwood cutting board. Stainless steel cheese knife with wooden handle, and a stainless steel waiter style corkscrew. It also has an adjustable removable shoulder strap with comfort pad and features four exterior pockets for extra storage. The Malibu comes in a wide variety of stylish colors and designs and is the perfect accessory for any beach trip, concert or casual outdoor event.
